            <p>
                The number of words in the novel <em>War and Peace</em>. Note that using an internet search, we found that sample pages of an e-book version of War and Peace have about 300 words on each page. This e-book version is 1307 pages long.
            </p>
        </statement>
    </task>
  </investigation>

